{"pii": "S0164121224001572", "abstracts": {"#name": "abstracts", "$": {"xmlns:ce": true, "xmlns:dm": true, "xmlns:sb": true}, "$$": [{"#name": "attachments", "$$": [{"#name": "attachment", "$": {"xmlns:xocs": true}, "$$": [{"#name": "attachment-eid", "_": "1-s2.0-S0164121224001572-si1.svg"}, {"#name": "ucs-locator", "_": "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/prod-ucs-content-store-eu-west/content/pii:S0164121224001572/image/svg+xml/34d7717dae7abd4cc11f935d3014efe9/si1.svg"}, {"#name": "file-basename", "_": "si1"}, {"#name": "abstract-attachment", "_": "true"}, {"#name": "filename", "_": "si1.svg"}, {"#name": "extension", "_": "svg"}, {"#name": "filesize", "_": "4280"}, {"#name": "attachment-type", "_": "ALTIMG"}]}, {"#name": "attachment", "$": {"xmlns:xocs": true}, "$$": [{"#name": "attachment-eid", "_": "1-s2.0-S0164121224001572-si2.svg"}, {"#name": "ucs-locator", "_": "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/prod-ucs-content-store-eu-west/content/pii:S0164121224001572/image/svg+xml/53085e242652e171c5a49505a32b9971/si2.svg"}, {"#name": "file-basename", "_": "si2"}, {"#name": "abstract-attachment", "_": "true"}, {"#name": "filename", "_": "si2.svg"}, {"#name": "extension", "_": "svg"}, {"#name": "filesize", "_": "2315"}, {"#name": "attachment-type", "_": "ALTIMG"}]}]}, {"#name": "abstract", "$": {"class": "author", "id": "d1e324", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e325"}, "_": "Abstract"}, {"#name": "abstract-sec", "$": {"id": "d1e328", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e329"}, "_": "Context:"}, {"#name": "simple-para", "$": {"id": "d1e331", "view": "all"}, "_": "Cloud computing\u2019s rise as the primary platform for software development and delivery is largely driven by the potential cost savings. However, it is surprising that no empirical evidence has been collected to determine whether cost awareness permeates the development process and how it manifests in practice."}]}, {"#name": "abstract-sec", "$": {"id": "d1e333", "role": "introduction", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e334"}, "_": "Objective:"}, {"#name": "simple-para", "$": {"id": "d1e336", "view": "all"}, "_": "This study aims to provide empirical evidence of cost awareness by mining open source repositories of cloud-based applications. The focus is on Infrastructure-as-Code artifacts that automate software (re)deployment on the cloud."}]}, {"#name": "abstract-sec", "$": {"id": "d1e338", "role": "materials-methods", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e339"}, "_": "Methods:"}, {"#name": "simple-para", "$": {"id": "d1e341", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "__text__", "_": "A systematic examination of "}, {"#name": "math", "$": {"xmlns:mml": true, "altimg": "si1.svg", "display": "inline", "id": "d1e344"}, "$$": [{"#name": "mrow", "$$": [{"#name": "mn", "_": "152"}, {"#name": "mspace", "$": {"width": "0.16667em"}}, {"#name": "mn", "_": "735"}]}]}, {"#name": "__text__", "_": " repositories yielded "}, {"#name": "math", "$": {"xmlns:mml": true, "altimg": "si2.svg", "display": "inline", "id": "d1e353"}, "$$": [{"#name": "mrow", "$$": [{"#name": "mn", "_": "2"}, {"#name": "mspace", "$": {"width": "0.16667em"}}, {"#name": "mn", "_": "010"}]}]}, {"#name": "__text__", "_": " relevant hits. We then analyzed 538 relevant commits and 208 relevant issues using inductive and deductive coding and corroborated findings with discussions from Stack Overflow."}]}]}, {"#name": "abstract-sec", "$": {"id": "d1e361", "role": "results", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e362"}, "_": "Results:"}, {"#name": "simple-para", "$": {"id": "d1e364", "view": "all"}, "_": "The findings indicate that developers are not only concerned with the cost of their application deployments but also take actions to reduce these costs beyond selecting cheaper cloud services. We also identify research areas for future consideration."}]}, {"#name": "abstract-sec", "$": {"id": "d1e366", "role": "conclusion", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e367"}, "_": "Conclusion:"}, {"#name": "simple-para", "$": {"id": "d1e369", "view": "all"}, "_": "Although we focus on a particular Infrastructure-as-Code technology (Terraform), the findings can be applicable to cloud-based application development in general. The provided empirical grounding can serve developers seeking to reduce costs through service selection, resource allocation, deployment optimization, and other techniques."}]}]}, {"#name": "abstract", "$": {"class": "author-highlights", "id": "d1e371", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "section-title", "$": {"id": "d1e372"}, "_": "Highlights"}, {"#name": "abstract-sec", "$": {"id": "d1e374", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "simple-para", "$": {"id": "d1e375", "view": "all"}, "$$": [{"#name": "list", "$": {"id": "d1e377"}, "$$": [{"#name": "list-item", "$": {"id": "d1e378"}, "$$": [{"#name": "label", "_": "\u2022"}, {"#name": "para", "$": {"id": "d1e381", "view": "all"}, "_": "There is empirical evidence of cost awareness during software development."}]}, {"#name": "list-item", "$": {"id": "d1e383"}, "$$": [{"#name": "label", "_": "\u2022"}, {"#name": "para", "$": {"id": "d1e386", "view": "all"}, "_": "Developers are aware of cloud-based software costs pre- and post-deployment."}]}, {"#name": "list-item", "$": {"id": "d1e388"}, "$$": [{"#name": "label", "_": "\u2022"}, {"#name": "para", "$": {"id": "d1e391", "view": "all"}, "_": "Commit messages and issue discussions show recurring topics on cost awareness."}]}, {"#name": "list-item", "$": {"id": "d1e393"}, "$$": [{"#name": "label", "_": "\u2022"}, {"#name": "para", "$": {"id": "d1e396", "view": "all"}, "_": "Pain points for developers include networking, instance, and billing choices."}]}, {"#name": "list-item", "$": {"id": "d1e398"}, "$$": [{"#name": "label", "_": "\u2022"}, {"#name": "para", "$": {"id": "d1e401", "view": "all"}, "_": "The identified topics are also prevalent in Stack Overflow discussions."}]}]}]}]}]}]}}